casebody.data:
Chugg-Carlin, Inc. v. Heckler Electric Co., Inc., et al.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs, unless the appellants procure the record on appeal and appellants’ points to be served and filed on or before February 2, 1960, with notice of argument for the March 1960 Term of this court, said appeal to be argued or submitted when reached. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Valente and Stevens, JJ.
